cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Gorgon"
authors:
  - name: "enchanted-plugins"
abstract: >
  Gazes at the repository, freezes its current structure into an immutable
  snapshot, and surfaces hotspots, cycles, and complexity by structural rank.
  Passive codebase intelligence orthogonal to per-change trust, workflow
  weaving, and intent anchoring.
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-04-25
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/enchanted-plugins/gorgon"
keywords:
  - claude-code
  - static-analysis
  - import-graph
  - pagerank
  - tarjan
  - mccabe
  - halstead
